during the break.

628
00:33:10,840 --> 00:33:11,580
But...

629
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:12,800
- Duang, are you...
- I'm free.

630
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:14,480
I'm very much free.

631
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:15,520
Mm.

632
00:33:15,860 --> 00:33:17,060
That's nice, actually.

633
00:33:17,420 --> 00:33:19,620
We'll tell Qin about the practice.

634
00:33:20,660 --> 00:33:21,700
That's excellent!

635
00:33:21,740 --> 00:33:23,020
Aww, thank you very much.

636
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:25,020
That's great. Thank you.

637
00:33:25,060 --> 00:33:25,740
Thank you!

638
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:26,500
Thank you, Alice.

639
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:27,780
Thank you, Tinn.

640
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:28,840
A round of applause, please!

641
00:33:28,950 --> 00:33:30,340
Come on. Thank you.

642
00:33:30,380 --> 00:33:31,020
Thank you.

643
00:33:31,060 --> 00:33:32,500
Thank you, thank you.

644
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:47,540
I miss you so much.

645
00:34:04,700 --> 00:34:06,620
Thank you for coming, guys.

646
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:10,219
We have something to inform you.

647
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:11,949
We requested the professor for

648
00:34:11,949 --> 00:34:15,520
