683
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,400
Wait. Stop, stop.

684
00:35:50,530 --> 00:35:51,280
Stop.

685
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:52,100
So...

686
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:55,400
Forget everything I just told you.

687
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:57,520
How many months
do you have for the practice?

688
00:35:58,580 --> 00:36:00,980
Until the next semester starts.

689
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:09,060
Qin, please practice
with him during the break.

690
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:11,920
I beg you.
At least three times a week will do.

691
00:36:13,820 --> 00:36:14,840
Good luck, boys.

692
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:17,540
Gosh, they're going to need it.

693
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,600
Excuse me.

694
00:36:20,640 --> 00:36:22,660
Can we leave now?

695
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,380
I don't think
both of us need to do anything now.

696
00:36:25,620 --> 00:36:29,020
If you think you're fine,
feel free to leave.

697
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:30,720
Okay.

698
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,140
Oh, by the way...

699
00:36:32,640 --> 00:36:36,580
If possible,
on the ceremony day, can we go first?

700
00:36:36,900 --> 00:36:39,100
I don't want to get embarrassed.

701
00:36:40,740 --> 00:36:42,060
Also...

702
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:45,060
They want us to perform,
not ruin the ceremony.

703
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:46,120
Do you know that?

704
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:56,140
Qin, please.

705
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:00,300
Sure.

706
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:04,140
