716
00:37:23,610 --> 00:37:26,590
Feel free to practice
on your own, you two.

717
00:37:26,870 --> 00:37:27,810
Okay?

718
00:37:27,850 --> 00:37:29,070
Sure thing.

719
00:37:29,450 --> 00:37:30,330
Okay.

720
00:37:31,850 --> 00:37:33,070
I'm going to use the toilet.

721
00:37:39,450 --> 00:37:40,530
Duang.

722
00:37:40,890 --> 00:37:45,550
I know that
you intentionally danced badly.

723
00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:47,910
No, I didn't.

724
00:37:47,950 --> 00:37:49,070
High-pitched?

725
00:37:49,330 --> 00:37:50,550
Is that so? Okay.

726
00:37:52,230 --> 00:37:56,590
The Faculty King I knew
still couldn't win Qin over.

727
00:37:56,630 --> 00:37:59,970
He was very dedicated,
yet he got rejected.

728
00:38:04,130 --> 00:38:08,470
However, it depends.

729
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:10,390
You might be that person, you know?

730
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:12,070
Huh?

731
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:18,090
No, you're misunderstanding me.

732
00:38:18,310 --> 00:38:21,030
What I mean by that is

733
00:38:21,070 --> 00:38:23,370
you might be compatible with Qin.

734
00:38:24,430 --> 00:38:28,110
From the bottom of my heart,

735
00:38:28,510 --> 00:38:32,670
I've been supporting
and rooting for you.

736
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:35,450
Good luck, okay?

737
00:38:35,870 --> 00:38:36,810
You've got this.

738
00:38:36,850 --> 00:38:37,590
Thank you.

739
00:38:38,190 --> 00:38:39,070
Let's go.

740
00:39:10,110 --> 00:39:11,990
Hey...

741
00:39:12,450 --> 00:39:13,370
What's wrong?

742
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:15,070
Is something troubling you?

743
00:39:15,970 --> 00:39:18,070
How did you know?

744
00:39:19,870 --> 00:39:21,030
You looked rather happy,

745
00:39:21,070 --> 00:39:22,070
so what the fuck happened?

746
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:25,830
I'm fine, actually.

747
00:39:26,330 --> 00:39:27,710
I feel better now.

748
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:32,530
It's because you were worried about me.

749
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:34,670
When did I say that I was?

750
00:39:35,750 --> 00:39:37,030
Fine, you weren't.

751
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:39,610
Asking me a question
already brightens up my day.

752
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:47,570
Come on...

753
00:39:47,610 --> 00:39:49,510
You don't care about me at all.

754
00:39:55,950 --> 00:39:58,070
[Qin started following you on Instagram]

755
00:40:00,210 --> 00:40:01,890
You followed me on Instagram?

756
00:40:02,390 --> 00:40:03,790
It's for discussing work with you.

757
00:40:04,130 --> 00:40:05,270
Don't text me pointless stuff.

758
00:40:07,070 --> 00:40:09,810
I'm delighted.

759
00:40:11,710 --> 00:40:13,090
Don't spam me with texts.

760
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,730
They annoy me.

761
00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:22,850
Are we going to practice or what?

762
00:40:35,270 --> 00:40:38,710
It'd be nice
to have someone ride with me.

763
00:40:38,750 --> 00:40:40,310
So you want me to go with you?

764
00:40:40,730 --> 00:40:41,990
Or do you want me to stay at your place?

765
00:40:43,830 --> 00:40:44,870
You and your nasty thoughts.

766
00:40:45,070 --> 00:40:46,130
Go home on your own.

767
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:47,610
I'll stop.

768
00:40:50,870 --> 00:40:52,090
I already called a ride.

769
00:40:52,490 --> 00:40:53,990
If you're tired, just hail a cab.

770
00:40:55,290 --> 00:40:56,710
I'll DM you on Instagram, okay?

771
00:40:58,210 --> 00:40:59,430
I already told you not to...

772
00:41:03,310 --> 00:41:04,090
Oh...

773
00:41:29,410 --> 00:41:30,570
Duang?

774
00:41:30,610 --> 00:41:32,130
What brings you here?

775
00:41:32,330 --> 00:41:33,510
Jamie!

776
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:34,830
What?

777
00:41:35,270 --> 00:41:36,450
What should I do?

778
00:41:37,250 --> 00:41:38,110
What now?

779
00:41:40,290 --> 00:41:43,030
Alice told me that
it's hard to win Qin over.

780
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:44,550
She also wished me luck.

781
00:41:46,570 --> 00:41:47,810
You just learned that today?

782
00:41:47,850 --> 00:41:49,430
I thought you already knew that.

783
00:41:52,090 --> 00:41:53,770
Alright. Serious talk.

784
00:41:53,970 --> 00:41:54,690
Listen to me.

785
00:41:54,730 --> 00:41:56,150
I think this is weird.

786
00:41:56,590 --> 00:41:57,910
What's weird?

787
00:41:58,510 --> 00:42:00,110
Alice is an outsider.

788
00:42:00,530 --> 00:42:04,150
If she told you that,
you'd better brace yourself.

789
00:42:04,770 --> 00:42:05,690
Jamie.

790
00:42:06,210 --> 00:42:07,990
How would that be possible?

791
00:42:10,430 --> 00:42:14,110
I know that you've been doing a lot
and trying really hard.

792
00:42:14,470 --> 00:42:17,950
But that doesn't guarantee success.

793
00:42:18,390 --> 00:42:22,110
Still, you might at least
get something out of this.

794
00:42:23,070 --> 00:42:23,990
Yes, yes!

795
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:25,630
Qin followed me back on Instagram.

796
00:42:25,850 --> 00:42:26,730
See?

797
00:42:28,530 --> 00:42:30,090
I could only DM him for work, though.

798
00:42:32,050 --> 00:42:33,330
You're really going to do what he said?

799
00:42:33,370 --> 00:42:34,090
No.

800
00:42:34,270 --> 00:42:35,970
I spammed him with emojis.

801
00:42:36,290 --> 00:42:37,030
Right.

802
00:42:37,070 --> 00:42:38,550
It's time for a wake-up call.

803
00:42:38,770 --> 00:42:40,610
You need to start thinking about this:

804
00:42:40,650 --> 00:42:43,070
if he rejects you

805
00:42:43,330 --> 00:42:46,610
or someone else comes into his life,

806
00:42:46,650 --> 00:42:48,110
you're the one who's going to get hurt.

807
00:42:48,330 --> 00:42:50,370
What are you saying?

808
00:42:50,410 --> 00:42:51,370
I don't get it.

809
00:42:51,410 --> 00:42:52,830
Gosh!

810
00:42:52,870 --> 00:42:54,070
You idiot!

811
00:42:54,730 --> 00:42:55,630
How about this?

812
00:42:56,070 --> 00:42:59,270
You're on a ship

813
00:42:59,310 --> 00:43:00,910
that is sinking.

814
00:43:01,070 --> 00:43:05,030
You can either
jump off the ship to end it quickly,

815
00:43:05,070 --> 00:43:07,890
or slowly go down with it,

816
00:43:07,930 --> 00:43:09,490
like Jack and Rose in Titanic.

817
00:43:09,530 --> 00:43:10,570
What will you choose?

818
00:43:11,310 --> 00:43:12,570
But...

819
00:43:12,890 --> 00:43:13,950
I'm on land.

820
00:43:13,990 --> 00:43:16,310
Yes, you are.

821
00:43:16,350 --> 00:43:17,750
You bastard!

822
00:43:18,870 --> 00:43:20,430
You never take anything seriously.

823
00:43:20,470 --> 00:43:21,350
I'm leaving.

824
00:43:24,690 --> 00:43:26,370
- Oh, Duang.
- Hm?

825
00:43:26,890 --> 00:43:28,490
- Take me home.
- No.

826
00:43:28,890 --> 00:43:30,390
Whatever.

827
00:43:31,430 --> 00:43:32,490
Damn it.

828
00:43:32,530 --> 00:43:35,070
Why would I be drowning, though?

829
00:43:37,650 --> 00:43:38,410
Damn it!

830
00:43:38,450 --> 00:43:39,690
He never listens!

831
00:43:39,730 --> 00:43:41,410
Staying on land is already safe.

832
00:43:42,090 --> 00:43:44,270
Don't pretend we're amphibians.

833
00:43:45,970 --> 00:43:47,410
Your words were so confusing,

834
00:43:47,450 --> 00:43:48,710
stupid Warrior.

835
00:43:54,790 --> 00:43:56,110
Speaker on!

836
00:44:22,810 --> 00:44:23,550
Hello?

837
00:44:23,830 --> 00:44:25,070
Hey!

838
00:44:26,070 --> 00:44:27,070
Why are you calling me?

839
00:44:27,710 --> 00:44:29,490
